      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">15.101-3</ph> 
         <?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2014-002?> Tiered evaluation
of small business offers.<?FM MARKER [Why] Add section 15.101-3.?></title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="id202SCF0D09M" class="- topic/p ">An agency shall not create a tiered
(or “cascading”) evaluation of offers, as described in <xref href="https://www.govinfo.gov/content/pkg/CFR-2019-title13-vol1/xml/CFR-2019-title13-vol1-sec125-2.xml"
                  format="html"
                  scope="external"
                  class="- topic/xref ">13 CFR 125.2</xref>, for
multiple-award contracts unless an agency has statutory authority.</p>
      </conbody>
